Class DetailedClassificationReport

  • java.lang.Object
    • pro.taskana.impl.report.Report<DetailedMonitorQueryItem,TimeIntervalColumnHeader>
      • pro.taskana.impl.report.impl.DetailedClassificationReport

  • public class DetailedClassificationReport
extends Report<DetailedMonitorQueryItem,TimeIntervalColumnHeader>
    The DetailedClassificationReport is a functional extension of the ClassificationReport. Its DetailedReportRows contain an additional list of ReportRows for the classifications of the attachments of the tasks.
